<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Email Verification</h2>
        <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with our service. Please click the button below to verify your email address:</p>
        <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Verify Email</a>
        <p>If you did not register for this service, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Thanks,<br>Developers</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>